text.tspan: > Hello?
> Is anyone there?
> My name is Jack. If you are reading
this, I am dead.
> Just kidding. But alright, I'll talk.
> I am a second year university student,
at UofT CS Software Engineering.
> During my spare time I like cooking,
listening to music, developing games,
playing piano, drawing, and building
random stuff (like this!) .
> But, let's get down to business
> My strongest language is Java, but as
of recently I've been enjoying Python
> I am learning Pytorch as we speak.
> My favorite web framework is Angular
> For comprehensive list, see repos.
> I've been programming many years now,
but still feels like I know nothing.
> Your ip address is 163.155.10.144
> I wish... I can't run scripts here
> Oh well, have a good day
( END OF TRANSMISSION )
